  "The Social Media Analytics Add-On helps you bring your YouTube, Instagram, and Facebook data into one central dashboard. Once activated, simply input the required credentials for each platform to begin tracking vital performance metrics. Designed to give you clear, actionable data, this Add-On makes it easy to measure engagement, reach, and growth across channels—without jumping between tools.": "De add-on voor sociale media-analyses helpt u bij het brengen van uw YouTube-, Instagram- en Facebook-gegevens in één centraal dashboard. ",
